                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The boots produced are mine, and what I lost that day.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence.</hi> This girl took the boots while I was speaking to Mr. Silvester; I did not know she had taken them; she went and pawned them, and asked me to go with her; she gave me the ticket; I took it home to my mother; I have not seen the girl since; I pawned them for her in my own name.</p>
